The film ’22 July’ was released on October 10 and was first shown in the 75th Venice International Film Festival. The film is a crime drama about the 2012 Norway atacks and its aftermath. It was written, directed and co produced by Paul Greengrass.22 July is a 2018 crime drama film about the 2011 Norway attacks and the aftermath of it. The film shows the mastermind of killings by an extremist who sets off a bomb in Oslo’s government quarter and proceeds to shooting 69 people in a youth leadership camp.